        "content": "<p>There you are - though <code>linarith</code> is a bit heavy-handed when you can use <code>exact hp</code>, and the fact that lean is willing to accept your <code>H</code> with <code>1 &lt; m</code> when the goal has <code>2 ≤ m</code> is somewhat of an accident</p>",
